        "Identify the problem statement",
        "Understand the given information",
        "Determine the unknown quantities"
      ]
    },
    {
      "Step": "Identify Relevant Concepts and Formulas",
      "Actions": [
        "Determine the relevant mathematical concepts",
        "Identify the relevant formulas and equations",
        "Consider any given constraints or conditions"
      ]
    },
    {
      "Step": "Analyze and Simplify the Problem",
      "Actions": [
        "Break down the problem into smaller parts",
        "Simplify the problem using mathematical techniques",
        "Consider any patterns or relationships"
      ]
    },
    {
      "Step": "Develop a Solution Strategy",
      "Actions": [
        "Determine the overall approach to solve the problem",
        "Identify any necessary mathematical operations",
        "Consider any potential pitfalls or challenges"
      ]
    },
    {
      "Step": "Implement the Solution Strategy",
      "Actions": [
        "Perform the necessary mathematical operations",
        "Apply the relevant formulas and equations",
        "Simplify and manipulate the expressions"
